              h: "The Keyword Funnel",
              body: "The comment-keyword mechanic — 'comment GROW and I'll send you the framework' — has become the standard creator lead-capture for good reasons stacked on top of each other. The comment burst reads as engagement velocity, which feeds distribution. The keyword is a micro-commitment (consistency bias from the persuasion stack, now working for you). And the automated DM delivery opens a one-to-one channel with a warm, self-selected lead — the single highest-converting real estate on any platform.\n\nCraft notes: make the keyword thematic and typo-proof (one word, capitals, no numbers). Deliver real value in the first automated message — the promised asset, no bait-and-switch, no 'first follow me and reply Y.' Hollow delivery poisons the well permanently.\n\nThen the pivot, one message later, permission-based: 'Curious — what are you working on that made this useful?' A question, not a pitch. The lead's answer tells you whether a sales conversation exists here at all."
